
Simplified instructions:

    1. Ensure you have the following software packages installed:

        fuse-devel
        libcurl-devel
        libexpat-devel
        libopenssl-devel
        pkg-config
        zlib-devel

    2. Either run `mkdir build; cd build; meson ..; ninja install` or 
       `./configure && make && sudo make install`

Please see

    https://github.com/archiecobbs/s3backer/wiki/BuildAndInstall

for more build and install information.
